						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">thefox wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">The idea was to set the tint bits as the very first thing in the fade, then after that just fade out normally.</div>
<br />What I tried (and didn't look good) was repeating these 2 steps:
<br />
<br />1. Set all emphasis bits;
<br />2. Clear emphasis bits and reduce the brightness of all colors by 1;
<br />
<br />We should keep in mind that the emphasis bits are problematic on the RGB PPUs.</div>

