					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I threw together a little demo to try out the RGB fade: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://thefox.aspekt.fi/palette-fade.nes">http://thefox.aspekt.fi/palette-fade.nes</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Press A to do the usual "subtract $10 fade". Press B to do an RGB-fade. Hold down START while pressing either button to add the 3 additional tint steps in the beginning.
<br />
<br />As to which one looks better, it's largely subjective, although using the tint bits definitely adds a lot of smoothness. I doubt an Average Joe would notice any difference...</div>

